Streetwise and sweet voiced: Carolyn Rodriguez is an artist whose music is forged from the gritty reality of her experiences and a powerful connection to her audience. Also known as Medicine girl, this soulful ballerina with a college degree, is an amazing singer and songwriter who believes music is like medicine for your soul, and any kind of mood you’re in there’s a remedy through music to overcome it. Her melodic sounds have graced many projects with many of our favorite legends and she has collaborated with multiple genres of music in Spanish and English. Through years of hard work, over 13 full length albums released independently and a tour bus later, she has been able to connect with thousands of fans through her music. Carolyn Rodriguez is here today to perform some of her newest music and top hits with her live band!

#legendaryhustle 13 years ago I dropped a mixtape called #BETTYCROCKER and I ain’t talking about the kind of cakes that your mamma makes!  me and my bro @therealmohustle (who did this artwork btw) were driving from Texas 2 Cali-AZ-Colorado-New Mexico and back pushing CDS, y’all youngsters don’t know about that cd hustle! there wasn’t social media with everybody buying and faking followers and streams; there were no streams. cd sales were at an all time low because people were downloading music for FREE off napster and other sites and burning their own so it was the hardest time in the music biz to be pushing physical product in the streets but they couldn’t deny the dope music and couldn’t knock our hustle no matter how many border checkpoints we got detained and questioned at for being on the road together, like she must be selling drugs, why else would she be driving around the country with tattooed up Mexicans 😂 thanks to every fan i met at every gas station and truck stop who supported and bought a cd so we could put gas in my car and get to the next town, you literally kept me GOING🤎🤎🤎🤎
